node.text:
Good morning 💨 I hope everyone is having a great morning. I’m trying to avoid social media and the news because is soooo much sadness. My heart goes to those 13 families who received the worst news imaginable these past few days. 
We definitely need to have an #StrongSoul 
Let’s also pray for #NewOrleans 💔🙏🏻
#AlmaFuerte
